data.description: This property is an exceptional find, offering unparalleled natural beauty and a unique set of amenities. The 360-degree views of Palomino Valley are breathtaking, while the 2-car garage with a workshop, private shooting range, and stamped concrete patio with pergolas provide both convenience and versatility. Whether you're looking for a space to entertain guests or you are an outdoor enthusiast, ready to off road in Moon Rocks NV turn this into your Oasis. The property offers both sustainability and convenience, with various off-grid features such as an underground water tank, solar array, septic tank, water spigots, electricity, and gas tank. Despite a fire in 2020, the foundation of the previous home remains, providing privacy while still being accessible to shopping. This is a rare opportunity for off-grid living in a stunning location only 20 minutes from Pyramid Lake! Cause of fire unknown.
